# 02 — Paid Media Platforms

## Main Platforms
- **Google Ads** — Search, Display, Shopping, Video (YouTube)
- **Meta Ads** — Facebook, Instagram
- **TikTok Ads**
- **LinkedIn Ads**
- **Amazon Ads**

## Campaign Types
- Search campaigns
- Display campaigns
- Video campaigns
- Shopping/Product campaigns
- App install campaigns
- Awareness vs Performance goals

## Targeting Options
- Geographic, demographic, interest-based, behavioral
- Custom audiences, lookalike audiences
- Remarketing (retargeting)

## Bidding and Budgeting
- Bid strategies: CPC, CPM, CPA, Target ROAS
- Daily vs lifetime budget
- Auction systems and Quality Score
